text: Osweiler is a small village Village d'Osweiller; retrieved 2012-4-26. in the commune of Rosport, Commune de Rossport; retrieved 2012-4-26. in eastern Luxembourg. The commune is in the canton of Echternach,Canton de Echternach; retrieved 2012-4-26. which is part of the district of Grevenmacher.CityPopulation.de, "Luxembourg, Grevenmacher", citing Le Portail des Statistiques du Luxembourg, Communes in the boundaries of Greenmacher, January 2012; retrieved 2012-4-26. The family of Dennis Hastert, the 59th Speaker of the United States House of Representatives, emigrated from Osweiler to America.Institut gran-ducal, "Dennis Hastert in Luxembourg"; retrieved 2012-4-26. ==References== ==Other websites== Category:Settlements in Luxembourg
